 - You're finally here.

176
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:52,940
I've been waiting for so long!

177
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:55,060
This is...

178
00:13:55,060 --> 00:13:56,980
Song Cong. He's my friend.

179
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:58,540
Hi.

180
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:03,320
