183
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:12,290
Your artwork is also on display?

184
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,888
What do you think of this exhibition?

185
00:14:15,888 --> 00:14:17,280
It's very interesting.

186
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:20,140
It's quite different from what I imagined a photography exhibition to be.

187
00:14:20,140 --> 00:14:21,500
