202
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:29,190
Song Cong,

203
00:16:29,970 --> 00:16:34,920
I can tell you're different from before.

204
00:16:34,920 --> 00:16:39,380
- I... 
 - Are you struggling with your studies?

