252
00:20:28,768 --> 00:20:30,780
It's fine. I can go back on my own.

253
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:33,180
- Waiter, can I pay the bill, please? 
 - I'll pay for this.

254
00:20:33,180 --> 00:20:35,273
